Omni (Symbol: OMNI) is a software layer generated on top of Bitcoin that aims at creating and exchanging customized virtual assets and virtual token. Omni transactions are Bitcoin transactions enabling next-generation changes on the Bitcoin Blockchain network. As an improved Bitcoin Core, Omni Core fulfills all the functionalities of Bitcoin and advanced Omni Layer features: 
+ Create easily customized currencies and assets directly on the Bitcoin Blockchainnetwork;
+ Blockchain-based crowdfunding; 
+ Buy and sell assets peer-to-peer on the Blockchain system; 
+ Easy to employ, guarded web wallets available; 
+ Fully-validating desktop wallet and client based on Bitcoin-Qt;
+ Easy to combine Bitcoin-based server daemon; 
+ Over 10M USD in asset market cap on the layer as of Feb '16
+ Combined with top Bitcoin and Alt-coin Exchanges; 
+ Tether Dollars supported by Bank Trust, redeemable for SWIFT at tether.to and bitfinex.com.

