ZERO (Symbol: ZER), as a branch of Zcash, has the security of Bitcoin, the privacy of Zcash and few other improvements. The coin consists of the best privacy and anonymity technology available today. The purpose of this fork is to examine the entirely different set of equihash parameters in the wild, selected parameters: N=192, K=7 these parameters should target available hardware for mining; and learn from it. This change develops all these parameters: 
+ higher time complexity- about 16 times; 
+ higher memory requirements- about 16 times; 
+ faster block verifications- 4x; 
+ smaller solutions-400 bytes instead of 1344 bytes are inserted in every block.
